GD/SIRDS version 0.01
=====================

Creates Single Image Random Dot Stereograms from a source image or depth
map.  Uses GD::Image objects as its input and output.

The algorithm for this module may be found at in an article for IEEE
Computer:

       Thimbleby, H.W., Inglis, S., and Witten, I.H.  "Displaying
       3D images: algorithms for single-image random-dot stere-
       ograms" IEEE Computer, 27 (10) 38-48, October 1994.
	

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  GD

